				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>Mozilla ? What's that ?</h2>
					<p class="fragment"> I can hear you saying-" I use it , Mozilla Firefox Browser " ! So , you mean this ?</p>
					<img class="fragment" src="https://mozorg.cdn.mozilla.net/media/img/contribute/firefox.png?2013-06" height="100" width="100">
					<p class="fragment"> If Yes , What's the logo below ?</p>
					<img class="fragment" src="https://mozorg.cdn.mozilla.net/media/img/contribute/dinohead.png" height="100" width="100">
						
					<p class="fragment" style="color:red;"> To clear up , Mozilla is global community that makes the browser called Firefox !</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>Mozilla a Global Community !</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Community of Volunteers and like-minded people</li>
						<li>Works to protect and shape the web even better</li>
						<li>Believes Web is the worlds biggest public resource and an assest of people</li>
						<li>Aiming for an Open Web for OUR goodwill </li>
					</ul>
				</section>
				<section>
					<h2>More About Mozilla ! </h2>
					<ul>
						<li class="fragment">Mozilla Foundation is a Non-Profit organization that supports Opensource Mozilla Projects</li>
						<li class="fragment">Mozilla Foundation apart from being a global community , has it's own subsidiary  </li>
						<li class="fragment">Mozilla Corporation (MoCo) which is taxable</li>
						<li class="fragment" style="color:red;"> Mozilla mission is to promote Openness , Innovation and Opportunity on the web (i.e) Open Web </li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2> Open Web ? What's that ? </h2>
					<p class="fragment"> Do you think we have complete control over today's Internet ? </p>
